+### Implementation Guidelines
+
+**Responsive Development:**
+
+```css
+/* Mobile-first media queries */
+.component {
+  /* Mobile styles (default) */
+  padding: var(--space-3);
+}
+
+@media (min-width: 768px) {
+  .component {
+    /* Tablet+ styles */
+    padding: var(--space-4);
+  }
+}
+
+@media (min-width: 1024px) {
+  .component {
+    /* Desktop+ styles */
+    padding: var(--space-6);
+  }
+}
+```
+
+**Accessibility Development:**
+
+```tsx
+// Accessible button example
+<button
+  type="button"
+  aria-label="Copy cover letter to clipboard"
+  aria-pressed={isCopied}
+  onClick={handleCopy}
+  className={cn(
+    "focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500",
+    "focus:ring-offset-2"
+  )}
+>
+  {isCopied ? <CheckIcon /> : <CopyIcon />}
+  <span>{isCopied ? "Copied!" : "Copy"}</span>
+</button>
+```
+
+**Semantic HTML Requirements:**
+- Use `<main>`, `<nav>`, `<header>`, `<footer>` landmarks
+- Use `<h1>`-`<h6>` in proper hierarchy (no skipping levels)
+- Use `<button>` for actions, `<a>` for navigation
+- Use `<ul>`/`<ol>` for lists
+- Use `<table>` for tabular data only
+
+**Focus Management:**
+- Trap focus in modals
+- Return focus after modal closes
+- Skip links for keyboard users
+- No focus loss on dynamic updates
+
+**Reduced Motion:**
+
+```css
+@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
+  *,
+  *::before,
+  *::after {
+    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
+    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
+    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
+  }
+}
+```
+
+**Color Independence:**
+- Never use color alone to convey information
+- Icons + color for status (✓ green, ✗ red)
+- Text labels for all icon-only buttons (via `aria-label`)
+- Pattern/texture alternatives where needed
+
+### Extension-Specific Accessibility
+
+**Shadow DOM Considerations:**
+- Ensure focus indicators work within Shadow DOM
+- Test screen reader compatibility with shadow boundaries
+- Keyboard navigation must pierce shadow root
+
+**Sidebar Constraints:**
+- Larger touch targets in compact space
+- Clear visual hierarchy in narrow width
+- Sufficient padding for accidental tap prevention
